{"attribution":"Occupational Safety and Health Administration, Keeping Workers Safe during Disaster Cleanup and Recovery, DTSEM FS-4355 08/2023, Chinese Simplified; no OSHA or U.S. Department of Labor endorsement or affiliation is implied.","cases":[{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-001","input":"在灾后清理以及重建时确保工人安全自然灾害可能导致洪水的大范围泛滥，并对财产和基础设施造成破坏。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-001","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-002","input":"清理和重建活动中蕴含着可能导致严重伤害甚至死亡的危险。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-002","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-003","input":"OSHA敦促从事清理和重建工作的雇主和工人了解这些危害以及如何保护工人。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-003","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-004","input":"下文概述了这些危害以及雇主和工人应当采取的适当预防措施。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-004","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-005","input":"如果您是参与清理和重建活动的雇主、工人、房主或市民，请务必在参与这些活动之前评估危险性和（或）遇到危险的可能性。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-005","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-006","input":"根据对危险的初步评估，雇主需要为工人提供适当的个人防护设备、培训和信息，以便工人安全地进行工作。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-006","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-007","input":"我们将会给您提供帮助。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-007","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-008","input":"被洪水淹没的工业和废弃矿场的有毒物质。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-008","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-009","input":"空气中的霉菌和真菌。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-009","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-010","input":"对封闭空间用新鲜空气进行通风。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-010","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-011","input":"除非有确实证据，首先假设洪水已被污染。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-011","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-012","input":"只有经过培训并配备适当个人防护设备的工人才能清理有毒化学品、其他危险废弃物和霉菌。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-012","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-013","input":"及时注射破伤风疫苗（最近10年内）。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-013","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-014","input":"扔掉被水损坏和明显受污染的物品。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-014","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-015","input":"使用防水靴、乳胶或橡胶手套和其他防护服装。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-015","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-016","input":"考虑使用特殊的耐化学腐蚀外套和护目镜。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-016","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-017","input":"在处理受霉菌污染的材料时，使用NIOSH批准的N-95或更好的一次性口罩。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-017","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-018","input":"保证充足且干净的饮用水和清洁用水的供应。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-018","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-019","input":"倾倒的电线接触与倒下的电力线相连接的线或物体（包括树枝）会有灼伤和触电的危险。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-019","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-020","input":"首先假定所有电力线都带电或仍旧通电。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-020","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-021","input":"在倒下的电力线路周围做出清晰的标记，以标示出危险区域。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-021","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-022","input":"与所有倒下的电力线路保持至少10英尺（3米）的距离。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-022","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-023","input":"只有经过适当培训和有齐全装备的工人才能修理电线。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-023","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-024","input":"树木的修剪与杂物清除与倒下的电力线相连接的电线或树枝有带电的危险，与之接触会导致触电。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-024","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-025","input":"被倒下的树枝砸中或压伤。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-025","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-026","input":"链锯和切割机等设备造成的伤害。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-026","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-027","input":"在抬起、移动树枝和其他碎片时拉伤和扭伤。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-027","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-028","input":"联系供电公司断电，并将电力线进行接地或屏蔽。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-028","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-029","input":"电力线周围10 英尺（3米）范围内的所有树木都需要修剪/移除，该工作必须由经过培训的树木修剪工来完成。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-029","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-030","input":"做出清晰的标记，以标示出树木残片可能落到工人身上的危险区域。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-030","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-031","input":"使用工作手套、安全帽、工作靴，听力防护和眼睛及面部保护装置。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-031","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-032","input":"操作链锯时使用护腿。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-032","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-033","input":"不要用端头进行切割。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-033","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-034","input":"不要太靠近切割机；严禁将手伸入正在运行的切割机中。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-034","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-035","input":"使用机械设备抬起重物。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-035","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-036","input":"如果不可行，请使用更多的工人和适当的举升方式。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-036","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-037","input":"潜在危险防护措施跌落工人从高空升降机、梯子、屋顶和其他高架工作台跌落。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-037","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-038","input":"在湿滑且不平坦的作业面，工人可能会因滑倒、绊倒和跌倒而造成伤害。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-038","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-039","input":"遵守安全规程，防止高空升降机翻倒。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-039","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-040","input":"使用系在升降机吊杆或吊篮上的坠落限位、作业限位或约束带。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-040","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-041","input":"遵从适当的用梯安全（如：梯子架设在坚固稳定的地方，上下梯时保持“三点”接触，不要站在最上面的梯级上）。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-041","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-042","input":"注意场地里湿滑的表面、障碍物或不平坦的地方。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-042","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-043","input":"便携发电机燃气或柴油发电机导致的电击和触电。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-043","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-044","input":"发电机废气中有毒的一氧化碳(CO)。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-044","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-045","input":"由于加油及燃料储存不当而引起的火灾。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-045","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-046","input":"严禁在室内或车库等密闭空间内运行便携式发电机。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-046","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-047","input":"检查电线以确保它们状况良好且没有破损；使用接地故障断路器 (GFCI)。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-047","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-048","input":"确保发电机运行的地方通风良好。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-048","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-049","input":"加油前应当先关闭发电机；严禁将燃料或发电机存放在室内。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-049","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-050","input":"作业区工人在作业区被移动的车辆和装置撞到，发生交通事故（导致伤亡）。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-050","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-051","input":"穿着符合ANSI/ISEA 107-2004标准的高反光服装和安全帽。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-051","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-052","input":"使用适当的交通控制（即信号、锥筒、分隔物）。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-052","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-053","input":"使用适当的照明、信号旗手和工地通讯。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-053","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-054","input":"确保车辆操作人员已经接受适当的培训。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-054","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-055","input":"始终使用安全带和翻车保护装置。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-055","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-056","input":"施工活动在拆除房屋和建筑物时，接触被石棉污染的材料。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-056","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-057","input":"进入受限的、有窒息危险的地方，以及其他的密闭空间。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-057","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-058","input":"沟和基坑的挖掘事故（塌方）。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-058","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-059","input":"人工搬抬及处理建筑材料和倒下的树枝时，可能会导致背部、膝盖和肩部受伤。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-059","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-060","input":"正确选择和使用个人防护装备（PPE），其中可能包括呼吸保护设备，同时遵守29 CFR 1926.1101中所列的其他程序。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-060","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-061","input":"未经培训和许可，不得进入需要许可的密闭空间。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-061","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-062","input":"相关的详细信息请参阅29 CFR 1910.146。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-062","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-063","input":"通过在构筑定边坡、边坡、撑柱或掩护支架来防止塌陷。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-063","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-064","input":"相关的详细信息，请参阅29 CFR 1926.651和1926.652。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-064","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-065","input":"使用适当的起重设备并由两人或更多人的小组来移动大件或重物。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-065","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-066","input":"DTSEM FS-435508/2023 Fact Sheet: Keeping Workers Safe during Disaster Cleanup and Recovery — Chinese Simplified 劳动者权益您有在安全的工作场所工作的权利。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-066","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-067","input":"制定《1970年职业安全与健康法案（OSH法案）》旨在防止工人在工作时受到严重伤害或死亡。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-067","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-068","input":"该法案要求雇主为雇员提供没有已知危害的工作场所。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-068","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-069","input":"职业安全与健康管理局（OSHA）制定并执行工作场所的保护性安全和健康标准。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-069","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-070","input":"OSHA还向工人和雇主提供信息、进行培训和协助。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-070","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-071","input":"如果工人认为他们的雇主没有遵守OSHA标准或存在严重的危险，他们可以提出投诉、让OSHA检查他们的工作场所。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-071","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-072","input":"我们将向您提供帮助。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA_FS-4355.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-072","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-disaster-cleanup-simplified-v1/sentence-073","input":"职业安全与健康管理局本文属于介绍OSHA计划、政策或标准的重点信息简报系列，它没有引入任何新的合规要求。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/defaul